                            Teacher and Mentor
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <p>
                            <b>
                                Allison Oldfield
                            </b>
                            <br>
                            Teacher and Mentor
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-caption">Social Media</h3>
                <ul style="padding: 0; list-style-type: none; margin: 20px">
                    <li class="overlay-social-object"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/VincentMasseyRoboticsTeam/" target="_blank"><img style="height: 40px" src="images/social/facebook.png"></img></a></li>
                    <li class="overlay-social-object"><a href="https://www.twitter.com/frc4903" target="_blank"><img style="height: 40px" src="images/social/twitter.png"></img></a></li>
